{"tid":1540602,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"同我一齊嗌 雙真普選 還政於民","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:02:37.000Z","uid":64298,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b4a28d2d4a384b225f4d45f411196872ff1ff78f","tid":1540602,"uid":64298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真雙普選</span></strong></span><br />\n先係真真正正將主導權放係香港人手上<br />\n<br />\n只要有咗<span style=\"color: gold;\">真真正正嘅雙普選</span><br />\n<br />\n另外個<span style=\"color: red;\">四大訴求</span>更有效真真正正咁去實現<br />\n<br />\n大家有眼睇所謂 <span style=\"color: red;\">撤回</span> 又玩語言偽術 又想呃鳩香港人<br />\n<br />\n你唔係仲信林鄭落命令嘅 <span style=\"color: blue;\">獨立調查</span> 會做到野吖？<br />\n<br />\n你唔係信中共會俾真正嘅 <span style=\"color: gold;\">民主</span> 你吖？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同我一齊嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真雙普選 還政於民</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">沒有暴徒 只有暴政</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"87eed9c223fc26f8b603c3a797779ad994bf5967","tid":1540602,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:57:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa37b8c3dc7e23ac9331a56d5ef8134bd3021019","tid":1540602,"uid":233982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fn8mK1C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFn8mK1C.png&h=142aa062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/042e41D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F042e41D.png&h=6821d7ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4361535f7a16816e79a647e8f7eb5ee4efe7eaf8","tid":1540602,"uid":64298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:57:42.000Z","msg":"打撚錯Topic添<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6b59451845e8fc068508bdb48ee2d299cedb8d","tid":1540602,"uid":128388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:58:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第六訴求</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7Yt9JA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7Yt9JA.jpg&h=c1d70329&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4okoYBW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4okoYBW.jpg&h=be2da638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2eb572146cbd18142b4351850ac12e3f8698d48","tid":1540602,"uid":64298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:58:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">真雙普選 還政於民</span></span>"},{"pid":"151982b3f470e27764ef1f269b0e188d9dcb434c","tid":1540602,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20